working on range values

x = range(22,3,-2)
y = x[2]
print(y)
for z in x:
    print(z)

Solution :
18
22
20
18
16
14
12
10
8
6
4
--------------------
range example 2

x = range(22,3,-4)
y = x[2:3]
print(y)
for z in x:
    print(z)

solution : 
range(14, 10, -4)
22
18
14
10
6

